  "texts": [
    "Unfortunately, no results were discussed.",
    "Moreover, Tyen et al. (2022) proposed a virtual assistant for second language learning with difficulty level adjustment in the decoder module and evaluated by experienced teachers.",
    "The system exploits RoBERTa fine-tuned with a Cambridge exams data set.",
    "The system attained Spearman and Pearson coefficients of 0.755 and 0.731, respectively.",
    "Finally, Wang et al. (2022) developed an educational domain-specific chatbot."
